      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DELATITE BEAST (1) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and four placings from 12 starts. Comes off a (22.39) win last time, scoring by 5.5 lengths in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 over 390m at this track. With a clean break looks hard to beat. RIPPER RILEY (6) finds it hard to break through. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (22.71) at Ballarat. Form here sound including four wins. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Winning chance. BOLD BERT (2) was in the minors two back (23.37) at Geelong but ran below best last time at Bendigo, finishing 8th. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from five starts. Can figure in the finish. ASTON MERRICK (8) is in the mix following a brief let-up.",
